## Quality checks before suggesting or publishing

- Examples copy-paste ready; expected outputs where useful.
- API docs: parameters (including optional), success and error examples, auth pattern, notable status codes.
- **docs.json** stays valid and matches [schema](https://mintlify.com/docs.json).
- Prefer verifying behavior against product truth over inventing endpoints or UI labels.
